## Agent Instructions

**Target crate**: `gbf-foundation`
**Target file(s)**:
- `gbf-foundation/src/lib.rs` (re-exports)
- `gbf-foundation/src/hash.rs` (Hash256)
- `gbf-foundation/src/cost.rs` (ByteCost)
